  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Children develop anxiety during the induction of anaesthesia and video-games might reduce or
      alleviate it. We intend to conduct a clinical trial to study the effect of tablet-based
      interctive games on alleviating preoperative anxiety.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Children develop anxiety during the induction of anaesthesia and video-games might reduce or
      alleviate it. We intend to conduct a clinical trial to study the effect of tablet-based
      interctive games on alleviating preoperative anxiety.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
